metadata.name: Nature is Dream
metadata.description:
Their ancestors' misuse of Hi-Tech destroys nature, resulting in the absence of ecosystems for plants and animals. Nature only exist in dreams and in metaverse world.
In that era, a tree is more valuable than a human. Nat always imagine the atmosphere and the true beauty of nature that has never been felt before. 
She is trying to save the last tree to save nature and future generations. 

size: 3500 x 4200
300 dpi - PNG
